  <lyrics>[V1]
 Dios yuspagarsmawa
 Nayar munatamat
 Take chuymajjampiw
 Jumar arcan munta.
 :Suma Dios Awquejja
 Nayar yatichitay
 Juman arunacam
 Parlañajjataqui. (Bis)
 
[V2]
 Khespiyirisajja
 Cruzan jiwawayi.
 Juchanacas laycuw
 Wilap wartawayi.
 :Jumajj iyawsamay
 Cristojj perdonätam
 Take juchanacam
 K'oma wilapampi. (Bis)
 
[V3]
 Cristojj mä uruwa
 Wastat cutinjjani
 ¡Cunja sumänisa
 Jupar uñe ataña!
 :¿ Juman chuymamasti
 Juchat k'omachatat
 Jupamp sarjjañatac
 Alajjpach marcaru? (Bis)
 
 </lyrics></song>